features: RAZOR-SHARP BLADES FOR EFFORTLESS GROOMING. Engineered with high-precision stainless steel blades, professional dog grooming clippers stay sharper longer, ensuring smooth and efficient trimming. The skin-friendly design glides through even thick, curly, or matted fur without pulling or clogging. Enjoy a seamless, high-performance grooming experience that lasts, making it the perfect tool for dog owners and professional groomers.

ULTRA-QUIET OPERATION. Does your pet get nervous during grooming? Our low-noise dog grooming clippers operate at less than 58 dB, significantly reducing anxiety and stress. The advanced noise reduction technology and low-vibration motor create a calm and soothing experience, making it ideal for nervous pets, puppies, and senior dogs. Keep your pet relaxed while achieving a professional-grade grooming result at home!

CORDLESS CONVENIENCE. The dog grooming clippers come with a rechargeable battery, offering 60–70 minutes of uninterrupted grooming time with a 3–4 hour charging duration. If needed, a corded option is also available! Enjoy total flexibility and freedom while grooming your pet with the dog clippers, designed for smooth, effortless trimming and professional pet care at home.

PREMIUM QUALITY ASSURANCE. Crafted from high-quality materials, these electric dog grooming clippers guarantee top-tier performance. No unexpected power loss, clogging from pet hair, or interruptions—just a smooth grooming experience. The dog grooming kit is built for durability, making it a trusted choice for professional groomers and pet owners who demand reliability and efficiency.

COMPLETE PROFESSIONAL DOG GROOMING KIT. This complete grooming package includes 1 professional dog clipper with blade, 1 rechargeable battery, 6 detachable guide combs, 1 cleaning brush, 1 stainless steel scissor, 1 stainless steel comb, 1 nail clipper, 1 nail file, and 1 user manual. Designed for even the thickest coats, this dog grooming kit ensures precision and convenience for professional and home use.
